    eyebrow: "Agenda control",
    title: "Visual timeline scheduling that stays usable when agendas get dense",
    desc: "Build multi-day, multi-room agendas with a view that stays readable for event teams, speakers, and operators. Session edits happen where the schedule already lives, not in disconnected tools.",
